Titolo: Kool-Aid Man (video game)

Anno: 1983

Descrizione: Kool-Aid Man is a video game for the Atari 2600 and Intellivision. Both were published by Mattel in 1983 (under the M Network label for the Atari version), but each game is of unique design. They are centered on the Kool-Aid Man, the television mascot of the beverage Kool-Aid.
Initially available exclusively through mail-order, it was later released through traditional retail outlets.